# myservice.yml:

apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: mynodeportservice
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
      app: myapp
  ports:
   - protocol: TCP
     port: 80
     targetPort: 80
     nodePort: 30001


# Instructions to Use:

- Create a myservice.yml file.
- To create service using that file:
kubectl apply -f myservice.yml
- To view list of services:
kubectl get services
- To check working of service on browesr:
-On powershell:
kubectl exec -it nginxpod -- /bin/bash
cd /usr/share/nginx/html
touch new.html
echo "diuuuuu" > new.html
-Inside Security Group of Worker Node add port no 30001.
-On Browser:
Search its public ip on browser

